couldn't have saved her.

18:27.481 --> 18:29.062
Has it saved you?

18:33.195 --> 18:35.356
Yeah.

18:35.531 --> 18:38.694
Young Benjamin will become
an important member of my court.

18:38.867 --> 18:41.859
lneed
the boy to...

18:43.122 --> 18:44.453
I need him to live.

18:46.708 --> 18:48.960
Please.

18:51.713 --> 18:53.294
Okay.

18:55.884 --> 18:58.261
(laughs)

18:58.428 --> 19:01.920
The Kingdom is favored
by your presence once more!

